{
  "stem": "15540.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And his grave is in the memorial park for-- for those who died during the war, which is close to my home in, in the suburb of Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I, I just remember there were some men there who were very helpful, and, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But obviously they, they and the fishermen all put their lives in danger to help us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was not taken at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was taken later, on another--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the 2nd of October.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by then, we had heard on the radio-- from the farm, actually, is when we heard-- that the action had taken place and that the Jews had been rounded up.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But because of, of the warnings, only about 400 Jews were, were captured in, in Denmark and, and were sent to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And out of those, almost all came back home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think less than 30 died in the process, which is a remarkable figure compared to, to any other country.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of those were old people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I knew one of them, a very old woman, who probably would not have lived anyway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the farm, we were preparing for this hunting lodge.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all I remember is that they said that there had been this action.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think this must have been the state-controlled radio, and it-- and that the announcement was just very brief and taut.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what we learned later was that there had been a-- what was called a razia, a, a, that, that the Germans had come to the hotel where we had stayed, two hours after we left, because they had been tipped off that there were Jews there.",
      "word_count": 47
    }
  ],
